ect1-function.odbc-exec-seealso">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <p class="para">    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link odbc_prepare()} - Prepares a statement for execution</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link odbc_execute()} - Execute a prepared statement</span></li>    </ul>   </p>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.uodbc.php">ODBC 函数</a></div></div>
